channel.title: ● Quest Booklet, The World Of Java Development Team ●
channel.description:
[center][size=13pt]● The World Of Java ●[/size] [size=13pt]● Quest Booklet ●[/size]
Welcome, i've decided to take my time to create a new development team. I'd like to call it a coding tour. The development team is going to go through some tricky jobs and we would like some help from you. I've taken some other time to create an official team website. You non joiners can also use it as a discussion or even a normal community forum.
I would like to see some interest.
[url=http://www.theworldofjava.smfforfree3.com][size=13pt]● The World Of Java Forum ●[/size][/url]
You've got to register, then send an application.
[url=http://www.theworldofjava.smfforfree3.com][size=13pt]● The World Of Java Forum ●[/size][/url]
Thankyou.
[size=13pt]● Slivion ●[/size]
The aim to a quest booklet, full![/center]
